{"abstract": "Users who mainly want a tablet that can sometimes be used a computer may be fine, but if you want to do intensive work, the Surface Pro isn\u2019t the best.", "web_url": "https://www.nytimes.com/2014/06/19/technology/personaltech/microsofts-surface-pro-3-isnt-for-everybody.html", "snippet": "Users who mainly want a tablet that can sometimes be used a computer may be fine, but if you want to do intensive work, the Surface Pro isn\u2019t the best.", "lead_paragraph": "FOR the better part of a month, I\u2019ve been trying to replace the laptop that I use for my daily work, an Apple MacBook Pro, with Microsoft\u2019s new tablet computer, the Surface Pro 3. I say \u201ctrying\u201d because that\u2019s what it has felt like; this is a machine that I\u2019ve had to put a lot of work into adjusting to, in the hope that, at some point, I\u2019d get used to it and see some kind of payoff.", "print_section": "B", "print_page": "10", "source": "The New York Times", "multimedia": [{"rank": 0, "subtype": "xlarge", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/06/19/business/19gadgetwise-web1/19gadgetwise-web1-articleLarge.jpg", "height": 405, "width": 600, "subType": "xlarge", "crop_name": "articleLarge", "legacy": {"xlarge": "images/2014/06/19/business/19gadgetwise-web1/19gadgetwise-web1-articleLarge.jpg", "xlargewidth": 600, "xlargeheight": 405}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "jumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/06/19/business/19gadgetwise-web1/19gadgetwise-web1-jumbo.jpg", "height": 691, "width": 1024, "subType": "jumbo", "crop_name": "jumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "superJumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/06/19/business/19gadgetwise-web1/19gadgetwise-web1-superJumbo.jpg", "height": 1382, "width": 2048, "subType": "superJumbo", "crop_name": "superJumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "thumbnail", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "i